Advanced Recursion Programs 

Recursion with Arrays:

Write a recursive function to calculate the sum of all elements in an array.
Implement a recursive function to find the largest element in an array.
Write a recursive function to find the smallest element in an array.
Implement a recursive function to print all elements of an array.
Write a recursive function to reverse the elements of an array.
Implement a recursive function to search for an element in an array.

Write a recursive function to count how many times a specific element appears in an array.
Implement a recursive function to merge two sorted arrays into one sorted array.
Write a recursive implementation of the Bubble Sort algorithm for an array.
Implement a recursive function to find the second largest element in an array.

Recursion with Strings :

Write a recursive function to reverse a string.
Implement a recursive function to check if a string is a palindrome.
Write a recursive function to count the number of vowels and consonants in a string.
Implement a recursive function to find the length of a string.
Write a recursive function to compare two strings lexicographically.
Implement a recursive function to remove all occurrences of a character from a string.
Write a recursive function to count the number of occurrences of a character in a string.
Implement a recursive function to convert all characters of a string to uppercase.
Write a recursive function to convert all characters of a string to lowercase.
Implement a recursive function to remove all whitespaces from a string.

Recursion for Mathematical Problems:

Implement a recursive function to find the least common multiple (LCM) of two numbers.
Write a recursive function to calculate the nth triangular number (sum of the first n natural numbers).
Implement a recursive function to find the sum of all prime numbers up to a given number N.
Write a recursive function to generate all possible permutations of a string.
Implement a recursive function to find the nth harmonic number (sum of the reciprocals of the first n natural numbers).
Solve the Towers of Hanoi problem using recursion (moving disks between pegs).
Write a recursive function to find all Pythagorean triplets (a^2 + b^2 = c^2).

Miscellaneous Recursion Problems :

Solve the N-Queens problem using recursion (placing queens on an NxN chessboard without them attacking each other).
Implement binary search recursively to find an element in a sorted array.
Implement the merge sort algorithm recursively to sort an array.
Write a recursive function to implement the quick sort algorithm to sort an array.
Implement matrix multiplication using recursion.
Write a recursive function to print all possible subsets of a set.
Solve the 0/1 Knapsack problem using recursion.

Implement recursive functions for preorder, inorder, and postorder traversal of a binary tree.

Write a recursive function to print Pascalâ€™s Triangle up to n rows.
Write a recursive function to generate and print all permutations of a string.

Implement a recursive function to print Fibonacci numbers up to a given number N.

Write a recursive function to calculate the sum of squares of numbers from 1 to N.
Decimal to Binary Conversion Using Recursion

Implement a recursive function to convert a decimal number to binary.

Write a recursive function to find all divisors of a given number.

Write a recursive function to find the greatest element in an array.

Implement a recursive function to calculate the sum of all elements in an array.

Write a recursive function to find the last occurrence of an element in an array.

Write a recursive function to find the depth (height) of a binary tree.

Implement a recursive function to reverse a singly linked list.

Write a recursive function to find the middle element of a linked list.